Package com.jaspersoft.android.sdk.client.async.request.cacheable

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CacheableRequest<T>
    A request that contains results that may be cached.
    GetInputControlsRequest
    Request that gets the list of input controls for the report with specified URI and according to specified parameters.
    GetInputControlsValuesRequest
    Request that gets the list of states of input controls for the report with specified URI and according to specified parameters.
    GetReportRequest
    Request that runs the report and generates the specified output.
    GetResourceRequest
    Request that gets the resource descriptor for the resource with specified URI.
    GetResourcesRequest
    Request that gets the list of resource descriptors for all resources available in the folder specified in the URI.
    GetServerInfoRequest
    Request that gets server information details.
    SearchResourcesRequest
    Gets the list of resource descriptors for the resources available in the folder specified in the URI and matching the specified parameters.
    ValidateInputControlsValuesRequest
    Request that validates input controls values on the server side and returns states only for invalid controls.
